            . I live with Mr. Ericus Robinson and his partner - they are <rs id="t18320705-134-viclabel714" type="occupation">calendrer</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320705-134-victim1180 t18320705-134-viclabel714"></join>s. On the 8th of June I found twelve yards of printed cotton concealed in a corner - I took it up, examined it, and put it there again; I told Mr. Robinson, who desired me to watch it, and on the 12th of June I saw the prisoner go and take the pieces of cotton, conceal it on his person, and go to the end of the street - I sent one of the men after him, to desire him to come back; he came, and was detained till the officer came.</p>
               <p>
            
